# Pre-push (THOROUGH gate — runs only when pushing, ~90s budget):
#   1. typecheck — tsc --noEmit on the PWA (excludes kindar-native which
#                  uses Metro extraNodeModules path aliasing; see
#                  tsconfig.typecheck.json). Catches use-before-declaration,
#                  out-of-scope identifiers, type mismatches that Next 16's
#                  Turbopack build does NOT flag. Critical — the bug fix
#                  4a83f02 (illness_episodes hospital_name) surfaced two TS
#                  regressions that had slipped past `next build` + `lint` +
#                  `test`.
#   2. test     — full vitest suite (currently 1115 tests, ~35s).
#
# CI re-runs both jobs (plus build + lint) as required checks on PR.
# Skipping this hook risks pushing a broken main; please don't `--no-verify`.
npm run typecheck
npm run i18n:audit-server
npm run test -- --run
